Package: cce
Type: Package
Title: Counterfactual Comparator Workflows for Survival Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Dai",
      family = "",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Author: Dai [aut, cre]
Description: Minimal workflows for counterfactual comparator work in
    survival settings. The package ships a compact demo dataset,
    a simple observed two-arm comparison workflow, a simple SOC-only
    projection workflow, and machine-readable output writers.
